verbose_text: The effect of H 2 O 2 / Cu (II) on the electrical properties of Retzius nerve cells in our study, seemed to be mediated by the HO *, as Cu (II), which leads to the production of this radical from H 2 O 2, and strongly potentiates the influence of an ineffective concentration (1 mM) of the H 2 O 2.
